{"tid":2219860,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩！微辣今次威到和任達華惠英紅呢D級數的明星去央視唱《我的祖國》！","createTime":"2020-09-27T07:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T00:56:46.000Z","uid":118346,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"46cf66856c6f7a47189a91b69e1c3020018b2828","tid":2219860,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T07:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hHu-xFyFgUUfbniaomXsrjfwKqY=/752x423/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2DAIT5F4CZHP7HQFZ4DJQUSZFM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhHu-xFyFgUUfbniaomXsrjfwKqY%3D%2F752x423%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2DAIT5F4CZHP7HQFZ4DJQUSZFM.png&h=4b01dbbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最左邊第一個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共將於10.1慶祝建政71周年，官媒央視按照慣例，於9月30日舉辦晚會，其中，多次高喊「我是中國人」的台星歐陽娜娜也在表演名單，她將與港星任達華、惠英紅，大陸明星杜江、童瑤、麥嘉欣及馬龍合唱開場曲《我的祖國》。<br />\n<br />\n身穿紅色禮服的歐陽娜娜受訪時表示，「大家一起合唱，又是一種特別澎湃的方式，覺得期待又激動，同時也挺興奮」。20歲的歐陽娜娜是國民黨發言人歐陽龍之女，近年積極在大陸發展演藝事。<br />\n<br />\n參與演出的台星，還包含在大陸發展有成的張韶涵，她將與港星陳偉霆、大陸明星張碧晨、關曉彤、吳磊、Soler樂隊的夏利奧合唱抗疫歌曲《守護》，張韶涵受訪時更祝福「祖國繁榮昌盛」。<br />\n<br />\n在台灣，陸委會呼籲台灣人不應參加「10.1」相關活動，因為中共安排台灣相關人士與會，目的是宣傳其「一國兩制台灣方案」 ，陸委會將密切關注相關情況，倘有涉及違反兩岸條例相關規定，將依法查處。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會指，中共去年提出「習五條」後，台方續修訂《國安五法》及《反滲透法》，當時有輿論指，法條定義模糊，影響兩岸交流。不過，陸委會主委陳明通則澄清，《反滲透法》是反滲透，不會影響兩岸交流，反而是保障了兩岸交流正常化，讓兩岸在經商、就學、旅遊與宗教等方面的交流，都能回歸單純的初衷。<br />\n<br />\n從宣佈海報來看，在晚會表演的也有不少港星，包括任達華、惠英紅、陳偉霆、容祖兒、楊穎（Angelababy），被大陸視為抗疫功臣的鍾南山也會出席。"},{"pid":"ad0a2f93f990297b4aade6f23ee25c059f621e87","tid":2219860,"uid":118346,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T07:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3368448/org/cddb3fa0b4ecca131158638eb1ab6d02.PNG/xcOUqsdIYBpsGXKN6W8D3r7MUCG0-vmH5Ozg-OTs4Pg?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3368448%2Forg%2Fcddb3fa0b4ecca131158638eb1ab6d02.PNG%2FxcOUqsdIYBpsGXKN6W8D3r7MUCG0-vmH5Ozg-OTs4Pg%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=a53a3dab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4ee5370a52b16a8ed8d5b2d9fcf978e7a97fd66","tid":2219860,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"關佢澳門小姐事"},{"pid":"ad1b3517cfa8580ed575e0c32c3418441e4e414f","tid":2219860,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T07:48:13.000Z","msg":"呢個世界就係比呢啲狗閪影響咗"},{"pid":"889224f50c3a394dc7db3c40cf10464d32a62faf","tid":2219860,"uid":184987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:26:30.000Z","msg":"Soler樂隊的夏利奧？<br />\n陳啟泰？"},{"pid":"e36a57517fee6692ae7b5b2507350ab527d4055f","tid":2219860,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"原來已經封左 ig 唔俾人留言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffed4935c3bd104174d97e647e3ae0e31c25414","tid":2219860,"uid":167658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aYSKH6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaYSKH6Y.jpg&h=eed0e7a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71b50651cb9be85102ff404d570138d0d407530d","tid":2219860,"uid":278184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:23:09.000Z","msg":"姐係乜水？<br />\n好耐冇睇過微辣"},{"pid":"8531c68af8c92d38baf808de7b02c28a96456966","tid":2219860,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T23:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578a7